  "title": "深度｜Agent 2025 趋势，编排工具向左，自主智能向右，智谱 AutoGLM 沉思如何押注？",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/aUkGw3UVcQFAD6xnteEkAQ",
